## 📌 Project Overview
This repository contains a comprehensive data visualization project analyzing the **World Happiness Report (2011–2025)**. The objective is to uncover the key drivers of human well-being across 140+ countries. 

To demonstrate technical versatility and data storytelling, this project was built using a **dual-approach methodology**:
1. **Programmatic Approach:** Custom scripts using Python (Pandas, Matplotlib, Seaborn, Plotly) for deep data manipulation and high-resolution charting.
2. **Business Intelligence (BI) Approach:** An interactive, user-centric dashboard built with Tableau to allow seamless data exploration.

