💻 How to Run the Code Locally
Clone the repository:
git clone https://github.com/yigitozdmr/global-happiness-viz.git)
cd global-happiness-viz

Create a virtual environment and activate it:
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate  # On Windows use: venv\Scripts\activate

Install the required libraries:
pip install pandas matplotlib seaborn plotly openpyxl

Run the visualization scripts:
python part_a_visuals.py
python interactive_visual.py
